      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1769010962328,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "       Linguaggi da utilizzare:\n- FRONTEND: JavaScript (React)\n- BACKEND: Java (Javalin) \n- DB_RELAZIONALE: PostgreSQL\n- DB_VETTORIALE: Qdrant\n- DB_NOSQL: MongoDB\n- MESSAGE_BROKER: RabbitMQ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "       Linguaggi da utilizzare:\n- FRONTEND: JavaScript (React)\n- BACKEND: Java (Javalin) \n- DB_RELAZIONALE: PostgreSQL\n- DB_VETTORIALE: Qdrant\n- DB_NOSQL: MongoDB\n- MESSAGE_BROKER: RabbitMQ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
